--- a/README.md
+++ b/README.md
@@ -116,6 +116,34 @@ Learn more about [agents](https://opencode.ai/docs/agents).
 
 For more info on how to configure OpenCode, [**head over to our docs**](https://opencode.ai/docs).
 
+### Regression Reports (Dev)
+
+Regression runs are written to `logs/{date}{time}/` and each run contains `index.html`, `manifest.json`, `screenshots/`, and `video/`.
+
+Generate a report run package:
+
+```bash
+bun run --cwd packages/opencode --conditions=browser ./src/index.ts report generate --logs-root logs
+```
+
+Open the latest report URL:
+
+```bash
+bun run --cwd packages/opencode --conditions=browser ./src/index.ts report open-latest --base-url http://127.0.0.1:4096
+```
+
+Run regression e2e capture locally:
+
+```bash
+bun --cwd packages/app test:e2e:regression
+```
+
+Troubleshooting:
+
+- `no report runs found`: create a run with `report generate` or run `test:e2e:regression` first.
+- Missing screenshot/video warning in report HTML: confirm the run produced files in `logs/<runId>/screenshots` and `logs/<runId>/video`.
+- Report page not opening: verify server is reachable and open `http://127.0.0.1:4096/reports`.
+
 ### Contributing
 
 If you're interested in contributing to OpenCode, please read our [contributing docs](./CONTRIBUTING.md) before submitting a pull request.
